ce/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The visit to Paris by the 73-year-old is the latest in her phased return to public duties after being rushed to Southmead Hospital in Bristol on June 23, staying for five nights after being injured while out walking on her Gatcombe estate in Gloucestershire.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999272590712, \"rank\": 7.274094592089247e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southmead_Hospital\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Southmead Hospital\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southmead_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southmead_Hospital\"}, {\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\", \"score\": 0.9997087945775315, \"rank\": 0.000291289965011933, \"text\": \"Bristol\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\"}, {\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gatcombe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4619031962179127e-20, \"text\": \"Gatcombe\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gatcombe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gatcombe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anne's medical team said her concussion and head injuries were consistent with a potential impact from a horse's head or legs but her concussion meant precise details of how the incident came about are not clear.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1858, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\":